  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc4 :\"\u0db1\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba,\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0db8\u0dba \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d85\u0db4\u0dd2 \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0d8b\u0dc0\u0db8\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd2\"",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil Wickramasinghe: \"We need to protect law and order and rebuild the country together.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe made a special statement today (July 18) and said that the country's fuel distribution is currently being restored and the more important thing right now is to make a decision about the future actions of the country's political parties.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe said, \"The most important political question we have today is whether we will oppose each other and destroy the country or whether our parties will work together for the country and rebuild this country.\"",
        "\"We need to protect law and order and build the country together. We don't need years to build this country. We will be in a better position next year and I hope that we will all build this country together in the next two years.\""
      ],
